title: Alex Jones Show - Jun 25 08 - Max Pappas, Kevin Ryan, Richard Ga
description:
Alex Jones Show
June 25, 2008
Max Pappas, Kevin Ryan, Richard Gage, Kevin Booth

Alex welcomes Max Pappas, Policy Director of FreedomWorks, to talk about a Senate bill requiring online transactions to be monitored by the government. Alex also talks with Kevin Ryan, former engineer and site manager for Underwriters Laboratories fired for questioning NIST\&#039;s explanation of the WTC collapses. Joining Ryan will be Richard Gage, founding member of Architects and Engineers for 9/11 Truth. Finally, Alex welcomes Kevin Booth, director of American Drug War - The Last White Hope.
